text: Harald Riedl (born 18 August 1961) is an Austrian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
